00:36:25,853 --> 00:36:28,388
Kenapa kau jadi
brengsek pengecut begini?"

764
00:36:28,422 --> 00:36:31,291
"Tom, aku harus memintamu
supaya tidak menyebutku

765
00:36:31,324 --> 00:36:33,961
pengecut ataupun brengsek."

766
00:36:33,995 --> 00:36:36,229
"Baiklah, tapi kau menderita
kayak pengecut

767
00:36:36,263 --> 00:36:37,699
dan tingkahmu brengsek."

768
00:36:37,732 --> 00:36:39,366
Tom?

769
00:36:39,399 --> 00:36:42,335
Colt Seavers.
