00:36:58,853 --> 00:37:00,755
Baiklah.

775
00:37:43,798 --> 00:37:44,999
Kopi.

776
00:38:00,447 --> 00:38:01,616
Apa yang...!

777
00:38:31,946 --> 00:38:33,714
Kenapa kau kayak pernah kulihat?

778
00:38:37,484 --> 00:38:39,419
Di mana aku mengenalmu?

779
00:38:39,452 --> 00:38:42,123
Aku Iggy Starr,
aktris utama di <i>Metalstorm.</i>

780
00:38:44,491 --> 00:38:45,893
Aku pacarnya Ryder.
/ Oh.

781
00:38:45,927 --> 00:38:47,427
Kau main di <i>Metalstorm.</i>
/ Ya.

782
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,696
Hey, apa kau yang ada
di film <i>Carjacked</i>

783
00:38:48,729 --> 00:38:50,363
yang pria bernama Jack itu
mencuri mobilmu

